{"tid":2263080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"flatmate成日屙屎唔沖廁，點對付佢好？","createTime":"2020-10-29T15:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T02:26:22.000Z","uid":200860,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9036d0a8767dc5f9e0c6f4a296e63f00a92487","tid":2263080,"uid":200860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟有個支那肥仔flatmate,平時河水不犯井水基本上係0接觸<br />\n但係條撚樣成鳩日屙完屎都唔沖廁,就咁冚埋塊廁所板就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次我一揭開塊板就見到勁多廁紙同屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚大鑊係啲屎喺個馬桶度焗咗一陣之後臭撚到仆街<br />\n一揭開塊板啲臭味就好似龜波氣功咁轟入我個鼻,次次都爭啲嘔埋前幾日食啲嘢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個鼻而家好似壞壞地同埋次次揭起塊板都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下大家有冇類似經驗同埋我應該點對付佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有機會再補返幅圖"},{"pid":"34891bd754ac3559c5dcfe2cee7c2243b46be14e","tid":2263080,"uid":68471,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:01:55.000Z","msg":"Hello moto"},{"pid":"d9bacafa5b155236900c143c8e642dbd5d863d60","tid":2263080,"uid":258899,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"咪大家鬥唔沖囉,或者下次你又唔沖"},{"pid":"012140d6aad1bd31f99f9f862ae003ff2867c549","tid":2263080,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"喺成棟hall大字貼提醒佢"},{"pid":"f7e3c8b6a7af53f417df819864f1300babfeb756","tid":2263080,"uid":200801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"下次佢痾屎你跟埋入去幫佢沖"},{"pid":"3e982bcd3b1c58a14976f7ee5182f9254ea7a39c","tid":2263080,"uid":200860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34891bd754ac3559c5dcfe2cee7c2243b46be14e","tid":2263080,"uid":68471,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:01: